column5: Good luck with the new semester bhaiya!
Thanks Riya. Need all the luck I can get.
Mom is making parathas. She’s missing you.
Stop tempting me. I’m eating hostel mess food.
Anjali called me. She sounded upset. Did you guys fight?
Just a small thing. Don't get involved.
Did you check the mail? Your bank statement came here.
Don't open it! Just keep it in my drawer.
Why are you spending so much at 'Back Alley Cafe'?
It's a study spot. Relax.
Mom's birthday gift? We need to decide by tomorrow.
Let's get her that silk saree she liked.
Anjali looks so happy with that necklace. You did good.
Yeah. She deserved something nice.
Rahul... who is Priya? She’s tagging you in weird stuff.
Just a classmate. Tell Mom I'll call her Sunday.
Anjali's roommate said she saw you out at 2 AM.
She's hallucinating. I was in the lab.
I don't like the way you're lying to everyone lately.
Mind your own business Riya.
Are you coming for the wedding? It's important to Anjali.
I have a concert. I'm not missing it for her cousin's wedding.
Dad is asking why you missed Dr. Sharma's lecture.
I was sick. Tell him I'm fine.
Mom is crying. You haven't called in 4 days.
I'm busy Riya! Just leave me alone for a bit.
